divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving west on route 52, approaching Pine Bush, NY. I noticed "something strange" in the sky, and snapped the attached photo. I don't remember seeing the lights move or blink or anything. Fast forward to late April 2010...looking through my pictures on my cellphone, I found the pic I had taken and had completely forgotten about. I do not believe there is any "missing time" but can't be sure, as I have no memory other than a vague memory of seeing something strange and taking a pic, then not thinking about it until I found the pic on my phone in April... I posted the photo to a local UFO yahoo group. One of the members lightened it, and I am attaching that photo as well. I cannot explain. Thank you.
